


1. Installing & Requirements
    1.1 System Requirements
        Minimum: PHP 5.3.5

    1.2 Installing
        1.2.1 Via Pear
            HazAClass is hosted on PearHub.org
            To install:
                pear channel-discover pearhub.org
                pear install pearhub/HazAClass

